    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi @timkelty thanks for pushing the API :) As of now we haven't done much work combining instantsearch.js and the derived helpers. The derived helpers generate their own events that instantsearch don't listen to. The easiest way to do what you want is to listen directly to the result event of the derived and update your UI accordingly without using a widget. How does that sound?",
